      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "I CHOOSE YOU (4) resumes having tackled the good juveniles in Victoria last season, last seen in the Vicbred Super Series in November. He was a Melton winner earlier in that preparation and has been readied for his return with two trial placings here. DEEP LOVE NZ (3) broke when well in the betting last start but had recorded a minor placing to kick off his career here prior. Should enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position and Hart sticks. Only needs to get things right to be in contention. JET PLANE (2) raced just twice as a juvenile and both were in the Nutrien Equine series. Likely to have developed with maturity and was readied with two trials. Draws well so keep safe. MY HIGH PEAK (6) improved to place from a wide barrier here last week. Can progress further third-up.",
